Welcome to UC Browser
UC Browser (hereinafter referred to as "the browser") is an advanced browser for smart phones and tablets. Using our innovative kernel and cloud technology, the Browser is famous for its intelligence, speed, security, expandability and data-saving features. It offers the best mobile Internet experience when you are reading news and novels, watching videos, playing games, or even shopping online.
We are dedicated to bringing you a convenient and fast way to surf the web and the best browsing experience. By clicking on "Accept", you hereby accept and agree to our Terms of Use.
Your support means the world to us. Join our User Experience Improvement Program to help us build a better browser. Thank you!
